---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/seo/Breadcrumbs.astro";

const canonicalPath = "/booking-policy/";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Booking Policy | Happy Faces LA"
  description="Booking, deposit, cancellation, travel, and event policy details for Happy Faces LA."
  canonicalPath={canonicalPath}
>
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Booking Policy", href: canonicalPath }]} />
  <section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Booking Policy</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Cancellation &amp; Rescheduling</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">A $50 deposit is required to reserve your event date and is applied toward the final balance.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Deposits are non-refundable because the date and time are reserved for your event. If plans change, the deposit may be transferred one time to a new event date with advance notice, subject to artist availability.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">The remaining balance is due on the event day before services begin.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Travel &amp; Service Area</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Happy Faces LA is service-area-only and serves Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Bookings start at $150. Travel may be included or added depending on event location, distance, traffic, parking, and total booking size. Final pricing is confirmed before booking, so there are no surprise travel charges on the event day.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Overtime</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Additional time may be available if the artist's schedule allows. Overtime must be requested and approved before the scheduled end time.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">If approved, overtime is added to the final balance based on the services being provided and the additional time requested.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Weather &amp; Outdoor Events</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Outdoor events are welcome, but face painting, glitter tattoos, face gems, and balloon twisting require safe working conditions.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Client should provide a shaded, protected setup area away from direct sun, rain, strong wind, sprinklers, smoke, dust, and unsafe heat. If conditions are unsafe, services may need to move indoors, pause, or be adjusted for safety.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">For best results, indoor or covered setup is recommended.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Parking &amp; Setup</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Client is responsible for providing safe, nearby parking or covering required parking fees.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Please plan for a clean setup area with enough space for the artist, supplies, and guests. Difficult parking, valet-only locations, gated access, stairs, or long walking distances may affect setup time and should be shared before booking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
